          "headline": "Gaming Room Ideas: Level Up Your Setup from Noob to Pro","description": "Gaming has become a part of our lifestyle. The increasing popularity of Esports and a lot of people becoming full-time gamers has grown the need for a dedicated room to play games. It becomes a must for people who stream their game-play as it increases the overall aesthetics \u0026amp; affects the viewership. From choosing the right chair to selecting the correct wall colours, there is a lot when it comes to creating your perfect gamer’s den. In this article, we will talk about things that you should focus on while building your gaming room because it's all about levelling up, one game at a time. ",
          
